data.description: This charming property is a lovely 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with a finished basement, offering ample space and comfort. The interior features beautiful wood floors, adding a touch of warmth and elegance to the living spaces.    The home is well-maintained, reflecting pride of ownership and ensuring a move-in-ready experience. The layout is thoughtfully designed, providing a cozy and inviting atmosphere throughout.    Situated on a nice lot, the property offers outdoor space for various activities or simply enjoying the natural surroundings. The presence of a 2-car attached garage adds convenience and ensures secure parking for vehicles. Additionally, a workshop provides a dedicated space for projects or hobbies, enhancing the functionality of the property.    This residence is not just a house; it's a comfortable and well-cared-for home that combines practicality with a touch of charm.
